I often have an idea for a bhop map, make one level then get bored of it so I'll be releasing them all as short speedrun maps (Think of it as another collection like horseshit). Cool concepts but unpolished and short.

Here's the first one. Some mirrors edgey floating flat textures thing. Have fun and make sure you play with sound on!!

Works on autohop and scroll 100aa and maybe even 400 vel if you're a boss
